  "detailed_description": "A roguelite, dungeon crawler, where you move all objects at the same time, and the same types that touch - merge into one! Defeat enemies, level up, solve quests, unlock new things, upgrade your character, and cast powerful spells!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308890/extras/2f4a16c983c21057ac0a8e5a2596c75d.poster.avif?t=1715771791\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308890/extras/2f4a16c983c21057ac0a8e5a2596c75d.webm?t=1715771791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308890/extras/2f4a16c983c21057ac0a8e5a2596c75d.mp4?t=1715771791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzle Dungeon Crawler</h2>Discover a fresh mix of a puzzle game, a dungeon crawler, and a deck builder! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308890/extras/f8377732f699e960f9f417c4abf7b054.poster.avif?t=1715771791\" width=600 height=470 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308890/extras/f8377732f699e960f9f417c4abf7b054.webm?t=1715771791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308890/extras/f8377732f699e960f9f417c4abf7b054.mp4?t=1715771791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelite</h2>Each play is procedurally generated. You can make your next runs better with upgrades bought in the shop, unlocking new powerups with finishing quests, and progressing the plot.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Synergies</h2>I've designed the skills, upgrades, and crafting system to help you find out new builds and use them to beat the game.",
  "about_the_game": "A roguelite, dungeon crawler, where you move all objects at the same time, and the same types that touch - merge into one! Defeat enemies, level up, solve quests, unlock new things, upgrade your character, and cast powerful spells!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308890/extras/2f4a16c983c21057ac0a8e5a2596c75d.poster.avif?t=1715771791\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308890/extras/2f4a16c983c21057ac0a8e5a2596c75d.webm?t=1715771791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308890/extras/2f4a16c983c21057ac0a8e5a2596c75d.mp4?t=1715771791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzle Dungeon Crawler</h2>Discover a fresh mix of a puzzle game, a dungeon crawler, and a deck builder! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308890/extras/f8377732f699e960f9f417c4abf7b054.poster.avif?t=1715771791\" width=600 height=470 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308890/extras/f8377732f699e960f9f417c4abf7b054.webm?t=1715771791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308890/extras/f8377732f699e960f9f417c4abf7b054.mp4?t=1715771791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelite</h2>Each play is procedurally generated. You can make your next runs better with upgrades bought in the shop, unlocking new powerups with finishing quests, and progressing the plot.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Synergies</h2>I've designed the skills, upgrades, and crafting system to help you find out new builds and use them to beat the game.",
